thriller is still `` thrilling '' ! best pop album of our generation..bar none ... from the opening snare stabs of wan na be startin ' something on through the lady in my life ... this collection of songs puts the `` magic '' in ..you guessed ! magical ! sublime studio musicians , crafty songs and q 's executive duties , and of course mj 's one-of-a-kind vocal/song contributions and least not his incredible mastery of melody and groove..you have not lived until you hear this pop masterpiece..every song shines ! beat it..human nature ... and billie jean..i still listen to this album after 23 years ... it 's fresh , it 's vibrant ... and the beats do n't stop til you get enough